### ==========================================
### cart-app.http
### Test giỏ hàng qua API Gateway
### Cart endpoints không bật guard ở Gateway hiện tại (có thể không cần token),
### nhưng file này vẫn đăng nhập để lấy userId cho rõ ràng.
### ==========================================

@gateway = {{gatewayUrl}}

### Chuẩn bị user và product để test
@cartEmail = cart-{{$timestamp}}@example.com
@cartPassword = Test@123456

### 0) REGISTER USER
POST {{gateway}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{cartEmail}}",
  "password": "{{cartPassword}}",
  "fullName": "Cart Tester"
}

###

### 1) LOGIN
# @name loginCartUser
POST {{gateway}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{cartEmail}}",
  "password": "{{cartPassword}}"
}

###

@cartToken = {{loginCartUser.response.body.accessToken}}

### 2) ME - lấy userId
# @name meCart
GET {{gateway}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{cartToken}}

###

@cartUserId = {{meCart.response.body.id}}

### 3) Tạo nhanh 1 product để add to cart (không category)
@skuCart = SKU-CART-{{$timestamp}}
@slugCart = product-cart-{{$timestamp}}

# @name createCartProduct
POST {{gateway}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{cartToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "{{skuCart}}",
  "name": "Cart Test Product",
  "slug": "{{slugCart}}",
  "priceInt": 99900,
  "stock": 100,
  "imageUrls": ["https://example.com/cart.jpg"]
}

###

@cartProductId = {{createCartProduct.response.body.id}}

### 4) CART - Add item
POST {{gateway}}/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{cartUserId}}",
  "productId": "{{cartProductId}}",
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### 5) CART - Get (theo userId)
GET {{gateway}}/cart?userId={{cartUserId}}

###

### 6) CART - Update quantity (PATCH)
PATCH {{gateway}}/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{cartUserId}}",
  "productId": "{{cartProductId}}",
  "quantity": 5
}

###

### 7) CART - Remove item
DELETE {{gateway}}/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{cartUserId}}",
  "productId": "{{cartProductId}}"
}

###